271
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:15,820
Because? Yeah, right. Inequality, right?

272
00:16:18,780 --> 00:16:23,520
If you feel that if you're just a normal
person, the rich have all the resources,

273
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:26,140
it's very hard for you to advance.

274
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,620
So, why have children? Okay?

275
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,840
Now, North Korea doesn't
